Over the last 3 days, every single day, we have woken up with so much love and warmth from people across the country. 

In our wildest dreams, we hadn't anticipated that our brand will receive so much love from the entire nation. 

Last Thursday i.e. 16th February 2023, will go down as one of the most important days in our brand's journey. Thank you so so much for a fantastic response to our #sharktankindia pitch. We love you ❤️

Since the time we aired, our team has been working round the clock to make sure deliver on the expectations of thousands of people who have placed orders. 

In case you missed watching our pitch, please watch and support India's disruptive, safe, and effective oral care brand. As we said, "Colgate 2.0 India mein banega and wo hum banaegne".

Special thanks to @peyushbansal, @vineetasng & @namitathapar for believing in our story and trusting us. 

Really really grateful to each and everyone of you.
